Anxiety:

• Feeling of nervousness, fear or apprehension is normal before any examination, test or for a loved one
• Anxiety is a condition in which these feelings become excessive and start interfering with one's health  
  and lifestyle

Symptoms to look for:

• Nervousness
• Fear
• Breathlessness
• Lack of sleep
• Irritability
• Indigestion 
• Nausea
• Inability to remain calm 

Causes:

• Excessive stress
• Side effects of medication or illness
• Illicit drugs
• Withdrawal symptoms

Natural home remedy using almonds, milk, saffron and honey:

